'''great ape'''

# An [[ape]] of the subfamily [[w:Ponginae|Ponginae]], having a mostly [[hairless]] face, [[protrusive]] lips, hands with complex [[fingerprint]]s, and flat [[fingernail]]s.  Includes the [[gorilla]], [[chimpanzee]], and [[orangutan]].
# May be extended to include members of the family [[w:Hominidae|Hominidae]], [[human]]s as well as gorillas, chimpanzees, and orangutans.


